and-- well-- weakness also.

00:37:28.072 --> 00:37:30.280
Maybe by experience-- you
will reveal them in a test.

00:37:30.280 --> 00:37:32.510
But He will know
you pretty well.

00:37:32.510 --> 00:37:38.190
And he has to design your
work according to your needs.

00:37:38.190 --> 00:37:43.193
According to the best fit of
your abilities and the work.

