tic extrinsically.

00:38:03.420 --> 00:38:05.250
They love money, they
want to make money,

00:38:05.250 --> 00:38:06.250
and that's totally fine.

00:38:06.250 --> 00:38:07.374
There's nothing against it.

00:38:07.374 --> 00:38:08.470
It's their motivator.

